{"tid":2219394,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–貓隻會否因為捕捉老鼠而患上鼠疫","createTime":"2020-09-26T23:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T11:35:12.000Z","uid":38861,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bac80124d117035e607fef0cd564565d5dba0beb","tid":2219394,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:11:17.000Z","msg":"此命題由<span class=\"blue\">汪汪真鳩喂（#5523）巴打</span>提供，在此作出致謝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n貓捉老鼠，天公地義，警黑合作，違背道義。<br />\n在回答貓隻究竟會否因為捉老鼠而患上鼠疫（Plague)之前，我們先行快速了解一下鼠疫的背景資料。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tygCZKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtygCZKA.jpg&h=9fba4dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鼠疫至少釀成全球二億人的死亡，由細菌Yersinia pestis 引致，為1894年細菌學家Alexandre Yersin在香港鼠疫爆發時搵出，因此取其名字Yersinia命名（Ref1)；<br />\n同期亦有一名日本科學家同在香港相近時間分離出致病的細菌，但因報告內容有些許具爭議性的地方，功勞普遍被嘉許在前者身上。<br />\n<br />\n鼠疫在人類史上可分為三大時期，分別為：<br />\n<br />\n1. 第6-8世紀時期的查士丁尼瘟疫<br />\n(Justinian&rsquo;s Plague)<br />\n<br />\n2.第14-18世紀別名為黑死病的瘟疫<br />\n(Black Death)<br />\n<br />\n3.現代<br />\n(近期較為大型的一次為發生在2017年馬達加斯加，釀成202人死)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然鼠疫歷史長久，但疫苗研究側重在其他疾病上的關係，現時其實並沒有具高效力的疫苗在市面，不少疫苗還停留在臨床研究階段當中；<br />\n美軍在越戰所用的疫苗，效果被證實非常參差，而且大部份接種者均展示出強烈的不良反應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）雖然我們用上鼠疫在形容此疾病，但Yersinia pestis細菌其實是寄宿在蝨的身體裡頭，藉著蝨的幫助下傳播開去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/upAkc4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FupAkc4G.jpg&h=33e01ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受感染的蝨會寄居在囓齒動物身上，促使被咬的囓齒動物將會感染鼠疫。<br />\n<br />\n現今的Yersinia pestis細菌品種，相信是透過蝨與囓齒動物不斷的互相傳遞而演發出來。<br />\n<br />\n之於人類患上鼠疫的途徑，則主要是接觸受鼠疫感染的動物、遭受感染的蝨咬傷或吸入受感染的動物體液所致。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）鼠疫可以大致分為三大類，Bubonic plague、Septicemic plague及Pneumonic plague，其分別及特徵一律在圖中列出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mupw4bq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmupw4bq.jpg&h=496658d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）而非常遺憾的是，貓隻是可以因捕捉受感染的鼠隻而患上鼠疫的。<br />\n貓隻大多數的感染個案為Bubonic plague（Ref2)，主人有機會因為被寄宿在貓隻身上受感染的蝨所咬而患上Bubonic plague，但亦有個別個案因為主人與貓隻親吻，因而接觸貓隻口水而患上Pneumonic plague。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XLsOmYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLsOmYa.jpg&h=96162fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，圖中所列舉的徵狀只是概論，一切由專業獸醫診斷為最準，而治療的手法跟治療人的方式一樣，一般開上抗生素作治療，而有必要時亦可能會隔離貓隻3日或以上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>各位巴絲想到有趣話題的話，不妨在留言提出，話題有趣且我有能力講解的話，將會被製作成為深入淺出的題材。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0vo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=eb560e51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0vo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=af524f28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41435-019-0065-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41435-019-0065-0&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0vo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=bcd6cbe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41435-019-0065-0</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.merckvetmanual.com/cat-owners/disorders-affecting-multiple-body-systems-of-cats/plague-in-cats\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.merckvetmanual.com%2Fcat-owners%2Fdisorders-affecting-multiple-body-systems-of-cats%2Fplague-in-cats&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0vo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=c3fa6b06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.merckvetmanual.com/cat-owners/disorders-affecting-multiple-body-systems-of-cats/plague-in-cats</a>"},{"pid":"3350abe44afa0fea8fa76bcdf9d05c6eb5cef165","tid":2219394,"uid":134739,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:28:01.000Z","msg":"緊係唔會啦 係中都係都叫貓疫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862125e7fcb38b1bd1354c4fec983607843b6247","tid":2219394,"uid":134739,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"3350abe44afa0fea8fa76bcdf9d05c6eb5cef165","tid":2219394,"uid":134739,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:28:01.000Z","msg":"緊係唔會啦 係中都係都叫貓疫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:28:14.000Z","msg":"樓主pin this"},{"pid":"10c41e7e6a95309827b58d7de401950c755a5f14","tid":2219394,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:31:06.000Z","msg":"細菌/病毒入侵宿主 再控制宿主行為去傳播 好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bb6941b9951c4cd4eebab30e6277de8bf241f7","tid":2219394,"uid":267647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:45:21.000Z","msg":"高汁，支持"},{"pid":"5d0f80f6a5428a5e41fca14dae6124bf663ec534","tid":2219394,"uid":5523,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0364e8504aa9c14e48d109496e35eb72ec7fa534","tid":2219394,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:47:09.000Z","msg":"/pish"},{"pid":"ee32db1e54d37a418b3beed7ac583337a53975f0","tid":2219394,"uid":58642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434c4734830aa7864ca14174e70b0cfb6627c78b","tid":2219394,"uid":185434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:50:36.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e6716203b5d2db8463ba86cc1d6dbf42cd9f4b","tid":2219394,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3350abe44afa0fea8fa76bcdf9d05c6eb5cef165","tid":2219394,"uid":134739,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:28:01.000Z","msg":"緊係唔會啦 係中都係都叫貓疫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"當時應該冇乜家貓 唔係就唔會咁多老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077bdba8d6fb0f8254c5cfc3fb80bf6f4b0a67e4","tid":2219394,"uid":54582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"學野po<br />\n推推"},{"pid":"88322fbac30d403348726d73bfe67a2b834d1287","tid":2219394,"uid":18350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1dc7b74c1041c8f17d498a4c545b78525ef4b5","tid":2219394,"uid":140659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:03:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fd90836b54d98dd8c4d30945d9f479ccf37409fc","tid":2219394,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"10c41e7e6a95309827b58d7de401950c755a5f14","tid":2219394,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:31:06.000Z","msg":"細菌/病毒入侵宿主 再控制宿主行為去傳播 好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:07:08.000Z","msg":"依個情況無控制宿主行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，純粹靠宿主習性散播開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ada80e4ae156e76ac9fbc2d2931c16bee19de1f","tid":2219394,"uid":72354,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"862125e7fcb38b1bd1354c4fec983607843b6247","tid":2219394,"uid":134739,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"3350abe44afa0fea8fa76bcdf9d05c6eb5cef165","tid":2219394,"uid":134739,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:28:01.000Z","msg":"緊係唔會啦 係中都係都叫貓疫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:28:14.000Z","msg":"樓主pin this"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:10:25.000Z","msg":"pin你老尾"},{"pid":"08e22eece22104ddcc6365cbb01d809c6f893ba7","tid":2219394,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫蝨疫"},{"pid":"42da184fef4a24ab985d0fe2f7d75a8bb31a40c4","tid":2219394,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:16:30.000Z","msg":"咁狗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c85ca8c0916f57835cdcb166adea4ef2f1d202b","tid":2219394,"uid":2950,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"862125e7fcb38b1bd1354c4fec983607843b6247","tid":2219394,"uid":134739,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"3350abe44afa0fea8fa76bcdf9d05c6eb5cef165","tid":2219394,"uid":134739,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:28:01.000Z","msg":"緊係唔會啦 係中都係都叫貓疫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T23:28:14.000Z","msg":"樓主pin this"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:16:42.000Z","msg":"Pin你老母咩pin pin pin"},{"pid":"88b4f1a6fa78230c9ba992f79ce9d10d1cd1433f","tid":2219394,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:18:19.000Z","msg":"打得飛機多會唔會中精疫？"},{"pid":"84d75e9fd5bcc8eb201748fa609c3c3a80ba172f","tid":2219394,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"08e22eece22104ddcc6365cbb01d809c6f893ba7","tid":2219394,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫蝨疫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"可能因為大多數被認定為老鼠作為傳播者，其實Plague中文譯名正式應該係瘟疫，不過用鼠疫稱呼應該更之為傳神同易明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n有研究用模型計算老鼠未必是黑死病的主要元兇，兇手係人類的排泄物，不過引起一定的爭議性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e0f5ffccfcc1ffc4f7e9bbf1a3cfd27e0421d4","tid":2219394,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:20:57.000Z","msg":"點解去到人類就大開殺戒，點解唔可以好似潛伏係其他宿主到咁潛伏係人類身上？"},{"pid":"457673143c4918a68b8bcbcfbaf4df968f685e02","tid":2219394,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"42da184fef4a24ab985d0fe2f7d75a8bb31a40c4","tid":2219394,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:16:30.000Z","msg":"咁狗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"狗都有機會靠蝨傳播到人身上，但相對上比貓無咁易感染同出現徵狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b6fd6f4675308bbd654648bfb433325a051602","tid":2219394,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"54e0f5ffccfcc1ffc4f7e9bbf1a3cfd27e0421d4","tid":2219394,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:20:57.000Z","msg":"點解去到人類就大開殺戒，點解唔可以好似潛伏係其他宿主到咁潛伏係人類身上？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:26:26.000Z","msg":"其實囓齒動物中咗Plague都出現好多問題，蝨應該先係一個較為穩定的宿主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6bdf9c1da78f6d3efc02c944a72c5dd6fb98f0","tid":2219394,"uid":200743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:50:07.000Z","msg":"之前睇過話咩黑死病係因為宗教信仰唔鐘意貓，先搞到好多老鼠加重鼠疫"},{"pid":"9acc7e1fbe606e4bc0b3c86e024fd8bfc583c6f6","tid":2219394,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"貓成日周街咬佢啲曱甴會出事？"}]}